getEncoded

public byte[] getEncoded()
                  throws SshException
Returns the key encoded into a byte array as defined in the SSH Transport Protocol. 
The "ssh-dss" public key format has the following specific encoding:

  String         "ssh-dss"
  BigInteger     p
  BigInteger     q
  BigInteger     g
  BigInteger     y
